Matrox Logo Matrox Electronic Systems is a producer of video card components and equipment for personal computers and workstations. Based in Dorval, Quebec, Canada, it was founded in 1976 by Lorne Trottier and Branko Matić. The name is derived from “Ma” in Matić and “Tro” in Trottier. Source
